# 8. みんなと一緒に！

Miku & MEIKO: ♪————!! ♪————~~~~~!
An: Whoa...! Miku and MEIKO sound amazing!
Kohane: I've never heard anyone sing like this...! It's like I'm learning about a completely new style!
Toya: Yes, and KAITO did a good job with these remixes. They give off such a different impression compared to what we originally had.
Akito: Yeah. You can tell that he worked on them. They have this fun side to them. It kinda makes me want to start singing...
KAITO: Then, join us!
Kohane: Are you sure?
KAITO: Of course! Let's sing together!
Minori: Woooooow! You all look way too cute!
Minori: Oh, look! Miku's doing my part of the dance!
Shizuku: Len and KAITO are also spectacular. They both look very cool and bring such a powerful presence to the stage.
Airi: I had a feeling they were doing something in secret. I guess this is what they were preparing for.
Airi: Great show, you guys!
Haruka: It really is...
Haruka: You know, I almost forgot how much people shine up there...
Minori: Huh?
Haruka: Because we never get many chances to watch these kinds of shows as members of the audience.
Haruka: I mean, I know that Miku and the others aren't singing our songs and dancing our dances exactly like we did.
Haruka: But I guess this is what our fans see when they watch us perform.
Minori: Oh...
Minori: Yeah, I'm sure you're right...!
Minori: This is what we've been doing. We've been spreading hope to all sorts of people!
Shizuku: I think that's what Miku and the others are trying to tell us.
Airi: Hehe. Yeah.
Minori: Alright! That means we gotta keep doing more and more and more!
Airi, Shizuku & Haruka: Yeah! Yes!
Len: ♪————! ♪————!!
Saki: This is so cool! I can't believe they're really playing our songs...!
Honami: Yes, it's so thoughtful of them... At the same time, it's a little strange to be hearing someone else play them...!
Shiho: I mean, I'm not sure anyone else has played our songs before.
Ichika: This is incredible...
Ichika: (Miku put on an unbelievable performance during our last show, but Len's just about on par with her.)
Ichika: (I need to keep moving forward... I think that's the message they're trying to send.)
Len: ♪————! ♪——~~~~!!
Ichika: I have to keep trying.
Rin: ♪———— ♪————
Ena: This is nice. It's really soothing...
Mizuki: Yeah. Kanade's song was already really good, but this feels so...
Mafuyu: Warm...
Len: I guess this is what she's been focusing on...
Ena: I never would've thought she was practicing her singing. That's actually pretty cute of her.
Mizuki: Haha. Yeah! On top of that...
MEIKO: ♪————...
Kanade: MEIKO's voice is so beautiful...
Luka: To think that we'd also get to hear her sing like this.
KAITO: ...
Ena: Still, it's pretty rare of her to want to sing for others like this.
Mizuki: Did something happen?
Kanade: I don't know, but...
Kanade: This is really nice...
Miles: “Shao, I'm sure you already understand.”
Miles: “Magic is not what creates joy. Joy is what creates magic.”
Miles: “That is why you, Shao, were able to become such a wonderful sorcerer. It's because you were immersed in smiles, laughter and joy for so long.”
Miles: “No, not just you. Everyone here. They're all sorcerers in their own right...”
Shao: “Master...!”
Shao: “The lights went out... The horses and the flying rides... They've all just stopped...!”
Shao: “No, I don't want this to happen...! Master worked so hard to build this place for everybody here...!!”
Emu: You can do it, Shao!
Shao: “Wait, no... This is no time to be crying...”
Shao: “Everyone, please! Lend me your energy!”
Shao: “This was the last thing Master told me! Everybody here can use magic because you're all smiling, laughing and making this such a happy place...!!”
Shao: “I can't do this alone! I'm not as good at using magic like Master was, so please, lend me your energy...!!”
Shao: “Lend me your smiles, your joy, your magic...!!”
Tsukasa: Of course! We'll give you everything we can!!!
Nene: H-Hey, you're shouting right in my ear...
Shao: “Everyone...! Thank you...!”
Shao: “I'm gonna try, master! I'm gonna use this energy to make everyone smile...!”
Shao: “Please...!”
Emu: Wow...! Look, you guys...! Everything's so pretty!
Nene: She just lit up all of SEKAI...
Rui: This must've taken a monumental amount of time to get set up.
Rui: But it was definitely worth the effort... I'm staggered.
Emu: This is super duper wonderhoy!
Tsukasa: Indeed it is! What a wonderful show!
Miku: (The others are probably gonna have to solve a lot of really tough problems in the future...)
Miku: (And they might have a really, really hard time overcoming some of them...!)
Miku: (But...)
Miku: (I wanna keep doing everything I can for them.)
Miku: (I probably wouldn't know what to do if I were all by myself, but with KAITO, Len, Rin, MEIKO, Luka...)
Miku: (And...)
Miku: (The other Miku that's watching over us. We'll figure out a way! Together!)
